snippet.title: Park Beyond: Chicken Run: Dawn of the Nugget Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Can you create a theme park where chicken-obsessed visitors have the best day of their lives? The newest #ParkBeyond challenge be-hens here! 🐔🏃🎢

Chicken Run: Dawn of the Nugget DLC is out now. Watch the movie on Netflix and then peck it up today! ▶ https://bnent.eu/PB-ChickenRunDOTN
